      <title>Altice France 的信用评级将 CLO 降至危险区域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/altice-france-s-credit-rating-cut-deeper-into-junk-by-moody-s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级将 Altice France Holding SA 的信用评级下调至最低级别之一，此举可能对该公司债务抵押贷款债务造成严重破坏。]]></description>
